metadata.name: TRIPPY SPACE
metadata.description:
NFT + Original Canvas Painting
60x80 cm/23x31 in
Oil on canvas, luminous paint

Trippy space is a space of awareness and harmony, it is the infinity of the universe and the point of its creation, it is the present, past and future at the same time. 

Addictive details are inviting to look into their depth. Psychedelic, bewitching, reality-distorting images and bright colors hypnotize and fascinate, making a person feel like in a different universe.
